---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Quarterly Systems">
	<nav class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="flex justify-between items-center h-16">
				<div class="flex items-center">
					<a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Quarterly Systems</a>
				</div>
				<div class="hidden md:block">
					<div class="ml-10 flex items-baseline space-x-4">
						<a href="/apps" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-purple-600 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-purple-500/25 px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200">Apps</a>
						<a href="#knowledge" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-purple-600 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-purple-500/25 px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200">Knowledge Base</a>
						<a href="/waitlist" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-purple-600 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-purple-500/25 px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200">Contact</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
		<div class="text-center mb-12">
			<img src="/logo.png" alt="Quarterly Systems" class="mx-auto h-72 w-auto mb-8" />
		</div>
		<div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
			<p class="lead">
				Quarterly Systems is dedicated to helping organizations operate with greater clarity, speed, and adaptability. Our platform provides the foundational tools teams need to reduce complexity and translate strategy into execution.
			</p>

			<h2>Our Approach</h2>
			<p>
				We believe every challenge is an opportunity to design smarter systems. Quarterly Systems integrates proven practices with flexible technology, enabling leaders to streamline workflows, improve collaboration, and capture measurable outcomes.
			</p>

			<h2>What We Deliver</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Simplification</strong> — Eliminate friction and create transparency across operations.</li>
				<li><strong>Acceleration</strong> — Move from concept to implementation faster with configurable frameworks.</li>
				<li><strong>Adaptation</strong> — Scale seamlessly as priorities shift and markets evolve.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Our Mission</h2>
			<p>
				To transform ideas into resilient systems that drive sustained performance.
			</p>

			<h2>Our Vision</h2>
			<p>
				A world where organizations of all sizes can harness the power of adaptable systems to achieve lasting impact.
			</p>

			<h2>Our Founder</h2>
			<div class="not-prose flex items-start space-x-6 mb-8">
				<img src="/mike.jpeg" alt="Mike Merrill, Founder" class="w-48 h-56 rounded-lg object-cover flex-shrink-0" />
				<div class="prose prose-lg flex-1">
					<p class="mt-0">
						<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kmikeym/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-semibold">Mike Merrill</a> is the founder of Quarterly Systems. Known as the world's first publicly traded person, he has built a career at the intersection of technology, governance, and community. At Quarterly Systems, Mike brings together his background in media, startups, and experimental platforms to demonstrate the potential of adaptable systems in real-world contexts.
					</p>
					<p>
						His focus is on building resilient infrastructure, showcasing innovative applications, and positioning Quarterly Systems as a leader in operational clarity and rapid experimentation.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</main>

	<!-- Footer -->
	<footer class="bg-white border-t border-gray-200 mt-16">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
				<div class="mb-4 md:mb-0">
					<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">© 2025 Quarterly Systems</span>
					<br>
					<span class="text-xs text-gray-400">a <a href="https://kmikeym.com" class="hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors">K5M</a> company</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex space-x-6">
					<a href="/about" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900">About</a>
					<span class="text-gray-300">·</span>
					<a href="/waitlist" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900">Contact</a>
					<span class="text-gray-300">·</span>
					<a href="/status" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900">Status</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer>
</Layout>

<style>
	.prose {
		@apply text-gray-900;
	}
	.prose h1 {
		@apply text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8;
	}
	.prose h2 {
		@apply text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4;
	}
	.prose p {
		@apply text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed;
	}
	.prose .lead {
		@apply text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8;
	}
	.prose ul {
		@apply list-disc ml-6 mb-4;
	}
	.prose li {
		@apply text-gray-600 mb-2;
	}
</style>